#text=I went out to my backyard with the appropriate tools needed to plant my tree .
#text=I was planning on planting an orange tree as I could harvest the oranges once they become ripe .

#text=I started digging into the soil where my old tree used to be -LRB- but was unfortunately torn down as a result of old age and danger of power lines , but I got the clear to plant another tree if I had wished -RRB- .
#text=I then planted my several orange tree seeds into the ground , and started covering them with dirt again .
#text=I tilled the dirt over and around the planted seeds to smooth out the surface .
#text=I then took my garden hose and watered the area for about ten to fifteen minutes .
#text=Once I was done with watering , I made sure the seeds did not get flooded to the surface of the soil as a result of my watering , to which I noticed they had been finely secured underground .
#text=I put my materials away and went back into my house .
